
In this module you will learn to:
==================================

1. Create a Data Source for importing records
2. Load data into a staging table
3. Create a Transform Field Map
4. Auto Map Matching Fields
5. Mapping Assist
6. Change or set field values using a Transform Map script
7. Coalesce to detect collisions
8. Use a Transform Event script to update but not insert records



Step - 1:
=========

prepare a dataset for import to Servicenow Platform

importing datasets : 
CSV
JDBC
FTP
HTTP
XML


